<subSubSection pageId="35" pageNumber="36" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="35.[151,1436,158,653]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
REMARKS: There are two original spellings of this genus-group name in 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[1004,1194,432,458]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" refId="ref145931" refString="Rondani, C. (1863) Diptera exotica revisa et annotata novis nonnullis descriptis. Eredi Soliani, Modena. 99 pp., 1 pl. [31 December +] [The title page has &quot; nonnullis &quot; but page 1 has &quot; nonullis &quot;. This is the separate that came out before the journal version with a different title, here as Rondani (1864 a).]" type="book" year="1863">Rondani (1863)</bibRefCitation>
: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1863" box="[1205,1316,432,457]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Bellardia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1205,1316,432,457]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Bellardia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(page 81) and 
<taxonomicName box="[297,409,471,496]" class="Insecta" family="Tachinidae" genus="Ballardia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[297,409,471,496]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Ballardia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(page 81). Acting as 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[662,824,471,497]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">First Reviser</emphasis>
, we select 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1863" box="[955,1066,471,496]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Bellardia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[955,1066,471,496]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Bellardia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as the correct original spelling, which relegates 
<taxonomicName box="[460,572,510,535]" class="Insecta" family="Tachinidae" genus="Ballardia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[460,572,510,535]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Ballardia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<emphasis box="[600,615,510,535]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">q</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[622,635,510,535]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">v</emphasis>
.) to unavailable name status. 
<bibRefCitation author="Robineau-Desvoidy, J. - B." box="[1041,1372,510,536]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" refId="ref142413" refString="Robineau-Desvoidy, J. - B. (1863) Histoire naturelle des dipteres des environs de Paris. Oeuvre posthume du Dr Robineau- Desvoidy publiee par les soins de sa famille, sous la direction de M. H. Monceaux. [Two volumes published simultaneously]. xvi + 1143 pp.; and 920 pp. [11 January] [See Evenhuis et al. (2010 b) for details on dating.]" type="book" year="1863">Robineau-Desvoidy (1863)</bibRefCitation>
was published on 11 January (
<bibRefCitation author="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; O'Hara, J. E. &amp; Pape, T. &amp; Pont, A. C." box="[552,826,549,575]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" refId="ref130296" refString="Evenhuis, N. L., O'Hara, J. E., Pape, T. &amp; Pont, A. C. (2010 b) Nomenclatural studies toward a world catalog of Diptera genusgroup names. Part I. Andre-Jean-Baptiste Robineau-Desvoidy. Zootaxa, 2373, 265 pp. [26 February]" type="book" year="2010">
Evenhuis 
<emphasis box="[672,723,549,574]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">et al</emphasis>
., 2010b
</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[846,1033,549,575]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" refId="ref145931" refString="Rondani, C. (1863) Diptera exotica revisa et annotata novis nonnullis descriptis. Eredi Soliani, Modena. 99 pp., 1 pl. [31 December +] [The title page has &quot; nonnullis &quot; but page 1 has &quot; nonullis &quot;. This is the separate that came out before the journal version with a different title, here as Rondani (1864 a).]" type="book" year="1863">Rondani (1863)</bibRefCitation>
has not been accurately dated but (based on receipts of it by Italian scientific societies in early 1864) is presumed to have been published late in the year 1863, and surely after 
<bibRefCitation author="Robineau-Desvoidy, J. - B." box="[811,1135,627,653]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" refId="ref142413" refString="Robineau-Desvoidy, J. - B. (1863) Histoire naturelle des dipteres des environs de Paris. Oeuvre posthume du Dr Robineau- Desvoidy publiee par les soins de sa famille, sous la direction de M. H. Monceaux. [Two volumes published simultaneously]. xvi + 1143 pp.; and 920 pp. [11 January] [See Evenhuis et al. (2010 b) for details on dating.]" type="book" year="1863">Robineau-Desvoidy (1863)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
